{"tid":741250,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"擁有900萬粉絲遭網路攻擊！「少女時代」潤娥強勢發文回擊","createTime":"2018-07-13T13:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T16:20:04.000Z","uid":9573,"like":20,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a1cce1c79ecfc34a1fdecd2841be4a062bec86c0","tid":741250,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T13:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imagelab.nownews.com/?w=1080&amp;q=85&amp;src=https://rssimg.nownews.com/images/5b44350f49e7bf4adb96750f_201807101224.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimagelab.nownews.com%2F%3Fw%3D1080%26q%3D85%26src%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Frssimg.nownews.com%2Fimages%2F5b44350f49e7bf4adb96750f_201807101224.jpg&h=729e8371&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲潤娥IG擁有900萬名粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n南韓女團「少女時代」成員潤娥長相甜美，在IG擁有900萬粉絲大軍，人氣可見一斑。但她的高人氣，似乎被有心人士盯上，她8日在社群網站上透露，IG的密碼遭他人竄改，導致無法正常登入，讓一票粉絲相當心疼。<br />\n<br />\n潤娥在IG上透露，「不知從何時開始，IG的密碼一直被更改，不能登入，即便登出後再重新登入，IG就不能用了。」事實上，克羅地亞人口只得四百二十萬，是一九三〇年首屆世盃的烏拉圭後，人口第二少的參戰決賽國家，潤娥近期在海外舉辦粉絲見面會，原定7日要在IG直播、與粉絲互動，但卻因密碼遭駭失敗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.nownews.com/nownews_production/images/5b44350f4eeeb54b135a3f1d_201807101224.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.nownews.com%2Fnownews_production%2Fimages%2F5b44350f4eeeb54b135a3f1d_201807101224.jpg&h=1e15ac46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲潤娥IG密碼遭駭。<br />\n<br />\n鮮少生氣的潤娥也透露，中場線欠缺創造性令三獅只能靠死球數胡。其實不只是對瑞典之外，英格蘭每仗都有失球，就連其他網站被駭也時常發生，坦言「與粉絲交流的空間，經常發生這樣的事，已經好幾次了」。潤娥也說這次是因為擔心才說出來，並希望有心人士未來不要再繼續這樣做。"},{"pid":"a74dec6635cfc2639380190d08fda4f65ad99e83","tid":741250,"uid":34495,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T13:31:52.000Z","msg":"若有若無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a335e1a27b41fbfd74c44c38fc4f435a47dd9537","tid":741250,"uid":1880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T13:32:25.000Z","msg":"咁樣叫回擊？"},{"pid":"2992f21c15a6812d21456dd1e1488f67068f4984","tid":741250,"uid":47268,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T13:36:53.000Z","msg":"克羅地亞人口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd8028909a54d447e17db9deb9714fd847be9337","tid":741250,"uid":32952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T23:54:09.000Z","msg":"事實上，克羅地亞人口只得四百二十萬，是一九三〇年首屆世盃的烏拉圭後，人口第二少的參戰決賽國家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e8c183873c54b0b8412dc6171441377dc919f2","tid":741250,"uid":44318,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T00:10:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d96278b2567a6cd39b21e3a43defab489dad04","tid":741250,"uid":62822,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T01:31:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"86d490722bf6faf576606ec54e870cd724d71899","tid":741250,"uid":83802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T02:29:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2285d7807f5a53456cb0dc4c0b100bd9d44501d1","tid":741250,"uid":194630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T02:40:46.000Z","msg":"以為有幾把炮回擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be7f81de80b0aa81e80fd79309d7b72a0bcee8e2","tid":741250,"uid":63113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T16:20:04.000Z","msg":"3c真心廢"}]}